data.description: An Offer has been accepted contingent on lender approving short sale.  Seller's are still allowing showings for Back Up Offers.  Custom Buescher home with so many delights, from the oversized main suite, reclaimed oak mantle, and large kitchen island with under island storage and seating for six!  This unique home has a an open floor plan that spans most of the main floor to allow entertaining, with a beautiful fireplace anchoring one side and custom kitchen on the other.  There is a large den and full bath, laundry and mud room off the kitchen, 2 bedrooms on the second floor, with large walk in attic, full bath and a great loft area. The oversized, three car garage has heating and ac.  This is truly a must see!
